28
00:01:11,208 --> 00:01:14,375
- SO, LET ME GUESS. OUR ONLY
CHOICE IS TO HEAD BACK TO BASION

29
00:01:14,458 --> 00:01:16,500
WITHOUT ANY NEW
SUPPLIES OR REPAIRS.

