HOW CAN I EVER
MAKE ATONEMENT?

43
00:03:23,375 --> 00:03:26,916
- Emily: YOU CAN,
BROTHER. YOU CAN.

44
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:30,125
- YOU CAN IF... IF I OPEN
THE BAXTER GATE INSIDE ME.

45
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:42,375
- SARA? ARE YOU ALRIGHT?

46
