50
00:03:49,041 --> 00:03:51,291
- Carmichael: DON'T WORRY.
EMILY'S JUST FINE.

51
00:03:53,083 --> 00:03:56,416
- IT WASN'T A DREAM,
IT ALL REALLY HAPPENED.

52
00:03:59,791 --> 00:04:03,083
- DO YOU HAVE ANY PAIN ANYWHERE?
- I'M FINE.

53
00:04:03,166 --> 00:04:05,500
- GREAT! THEN WE CAN GET
BACK TO THE EXPERIMENT!

54
00:04:05,583 --> 00:04:08,208
