I THOUGHT I WAS BEING
HANDED OVER TO THE MILITARY.

57
00:04:12,916 --> 00:04:15,083
- THAT PLAN'S BEEN PUT ON
HOLD FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

58
00:04:17,666 --> 00:04:19,541
- Martha: WHAT A LETDOWN!

59
00:04:19,625 --> 00:04:21,958
- YEAH, WE WORK SO
HARD TO GET TO BREGMA,

60
00:04:22,041 --> 00:04:23,833
JUST TO FIND OUT THAT
NO ONE'S HERE TO HELP

61
00:04:23,916 --> 00:04:25,791
AND THE DEAGUE'S NOT
CHASING US ANYMORE.

62
00:04:25,875 --> 00:04:27,958
- ARE WE REALLY SURE
THEY'RE NOT COMING?

63
00:04:28,041 --> 00:04:29,666
- WELL, THE TIME LIMIT
WAS REALLY TIGHT

64
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:30,708
AND IF THEY WERE
GOING TO MAKE IT,

65
00:04:30,791 --> 00:04:32,041
THEY'D HAVE TO HAVE
GONE STRAIGHT TO

66
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:34,666
THE STAGING POINT
FROM GALL'S DEPOT.

67
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:36,625
- I SEE.

68
00:04:36,708 --> 00:04:39,083
- I'M TELLING YOU,
MY BROTHER WILL SHOW UP!

69
00:04:39,166 --> 00:04:40,416
- OH, COME ON NOW!

70
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:42,791
THEY'RE STAGING AN INCREDIBLY
MASSIVE OPERATION!

71
00:04:42,875 --> 00:04:44,958
JUST BECAUSE HE'S
RALPH WEREC DOESN'T MEAN...

72
00:04:45,041 --> 00:04:47,916
NO, ACTUALLY, THE FACT THAT
HE'S A PROVEN TRAITOR ENSURES

73
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,916
THEY'D NEVER ALLOW HIM
TO ACT ON HIS OWN!

74
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,791
SO EVEN IF HE WANTED
TO COME HE COULDN'T!

75
00:04:51,875 --> 00:04:53,208
- HE'LL DO IT ANYWAY!

76
00:04:54,958 --> 00:04:57,625
I'M SORRY,
BUT YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND,

77
00:04:57,708 --> 00:05:00,625
MY BROTHER IS OBLIGATED
TO COME HERE.

78
00:05:00,708 --> 00:05:02,541
- WAIT, LET'S GET CRAVEN.

79
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:09,750
- HE HAS TO, BECAUSE HE
MADE A VERY SERIOUS PROMISE.

80
00:05:10,958 --> 00:05:13,875
AND THAT'S WHY,
I KNOW HE WILL.

81
00:05:15,125 --> 00:05:17,791
- BEGINNING OUR THIRD
DECELERATION NOW.

82
00:05:17,875 --> 00:05:20,333
COUNTDOWN. THREE.

83
00:05:20,416 --> 00:05:22,416
