84
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,083
- ( rumbling and clanging )

85
00:05:24,166 --> 00:05:25,125
- ( groaning )

86
00:05:26,625 --> 00:05:28,125
- ( whines )

87
00:05:28,208 --> 00:05:30,583
- BROTHER!
- I'M FINE.

88
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:37,375
- Craven: SARA,
PLEASE TELL US EVERYTHING.

89
00:05:37,458 --> 00:05:39,041
EVERYTHING YOU
SAW AND LEARNED,

90
00:05:39,125 --> 00:05:41,291
WHEN YOU WERE
LINKED TO THE MIMIC.

91
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:45,875
- WELL, SIR. IT HAPPENED
OVER SIX HUNDRED YEARS AGO.

92
00:05:50,625 --> 00:05:52,541
THE SPACESHIP WAS INDEPENDENT.

93
00:05:52,625 --> 00:05:55,375
IT DIDN'T BELONG TO
THE UNION OR THE DEAGUE,

94
00:05:55,458 --> 00:05:56,541
BUT, IT LANDED ON

95
00:05:56,625 --> 00:06:00,000
THE UNION RESOURCE
SATELLITE OF NIEREN SIX.

96
00:06:07,875 --> 00:06:10,875
- THEY WERE ALIENS THAT
ALL LOOKED EXACTLY ALIKE?

97
00:06:10,958 --> 00:06:13,125
- THEY WERE REFERRED
TO AS UKs.

98
00:06:13,208 --> 00:06:16,833
"UNKNOWNS," AND THEY WERE PLACED
UNDER MILITARY SUPERVISION.

99
00:06:16,916 --> 00:06:20,166
AND THEN, THE RESEARCH BEGAN,

100
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:21,708
IN ABSOLUTE SECRECY.

101
00:06:30,250 --> 00:06:32,708
- UGH! THAT'S UNFORGIVABLE.

102
00:06:32,791 --> 00:06:34,875
- ONE OF THE IMPORTANT
THINGS THEY DISCOVERED,

103
00:06:34,958 --> 00:06:37,625
WAS THAT THE GIRLS ALL
SHARED SOME OF THEIR SENSES.

104
00:06:37,708 --> 00:06:38,750
- THEY SHARED...

105
00:06:38,833 --> 00:06:41,750
- Sara: SIGHT, HEARING,
AND EMOTION.

106
00:06:41,833 --> 00:06:44,250
- WHEN YOU SAY ALL
THE GIRLS, DO YOU MEAN?

107
00:06:44,333 --> 00:06:46,666
- EVEN LIGHT-YEARS APART
THEY COMMUNICATE,

108
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:49,125
WITHOUT ANY DIFFICULTY
OR TIME-LAG.

109
00:06:49,208 --> 00:06:50,541
- BUT THAT COULD
HAVE APPLICATIONS

110
00:06:50,625 --> 00:06:51,916
IN ALL SORTS OF FIELDS.

111
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:54,791
THINK ABOUT IT. INSTANT
INTERSTELLAR COMMUNICATION!

112
00:06:54,875 --> 00:06:58,041
- THAT'S THE POINT, IT WAS FOR
EXACTLY THAT KIND OF GAIN.

113
00:07:00,458 --> 00:07:02,500
ALL OF THOSE GIRLS WERE...

114
00:07:04,666 --> 00:07:05,666
- SORRY.

115
00:07:07,333 --> 00:07:09,666
SO THAT EXPLAINS
THE MIMIC EMILY.

116
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:12,875
SHE WAS ONE OF
THE ALIENS THEY FOUND.

117
00:07:12,958 --> 00:07:14,250
- AND, IF THEY WERE RESEARCHING

118
00:07:14,333 --> 00:07:15,875
INSTANT INTERSTELLAR
COMMUNICATION,

119
00:07:15,958 --> 00:07:18,083
THEN WHY ISN'T
IT POSSIBLE YET?

120
00:07:18,166 --> 00:07:19,708
- DO YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENED?

121
