- NIEREN SIX WAS NEVER INTENDED
TO BE A RESEARCH FACILITY.

122
00:07:23,041 --> 00:07:26,041
TECHNOLOGY COULD
ONLY DEVELOP SO FAR.

123
00:07:26,125 --> 00:07:28,625
SO, THEY DECIDED TO MOVE
THE WHOLE OPERATION

124
00:07:28,708 --> 00:07:30,458
TO PLANET GRABERA.

125
00:07:30,541 --> 00:07:32,666
- Carmichael: THEY'D BE FAR
FROM THE FRONT LINES THERE.

126
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:35,208
IT'S A PERFECT PLACE FOR
DOING SECRETIVE RESEARCH.

127
00:07:37,250 --> 00:07:38,666
- ( turbines whirring )

128
00:07:41,375 --> 00:07:43,416
- Sara: BUT,
ALMOST IMMEDIATELY...

129
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:51,750
- ( indistinct shouting )

130
00:07:51,833 --> 00:07:54,125
- Melchi: THE BAXTER GATE?

131
00:07:54,208 --> 00:07:56,625
- Sara: A GATE THAT
CONNECTS LOCATIONS IN SPACE,

132
00:07:57,416 --> 00:07:59,625
AND OUT OF IT CAME...

133
00:08:05,166 --> 00:08:07,375
- Dufarge: THEY CAME TO
RETRIEVE THEIR COMRADES.

134
00:08:11,833 --> 00:08:13,166
- Ben: INCREDIBLE.

135
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:16,458
A SUB-LIGHTSPEED BATTLE IN
AN ERA WITHOUT STRAINS.

136
00:08:16,541 --> 00:08:18,291
THE UNION'S ONLY
OPTION WOULD BE TO RUN.

137
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:24,333
- Melchi: BUT THERE WOULD
BE ONE WAY TO SURVIVE.

138
00:08:25,833 --> 00:08:28,541
SEND AS MUCH OF THE RESEARCH
AS POSSIBLE TO GRABERA

139
00:08:28,625 --> 00:08:31,666
AND USE IT TO CREATE A WEAPON
CAPABLE OF DEFEATING THEM.

140
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:34,041
- YEAH! A FEW HOURS
OF SUB-LIGHTSPEED TRAVEL

141
