WOULD EQUAL CENTURIES
OF OBJECTIVE TIME!

142
00:08:36,708 --> 00:08:37,958
- IF THINGS GO WELL,

143
00:08:38,041 --> 00:08:40,250
REINFORCEMENTS COULD BE
ARRIVING IN MERE MINUTES!

144
00:08:40,333 --> 00:08:41,625
- THEN WHAT WE'RE SAYING IS

145
00:08:41,708 --> 00:08:43,708
THAT'S HOW STRAIN TECHNOLOGY
CAME TO BE DEVELOPED.

146
00:08:43,791 --> 00:08:45,083
- YES.

147
00:08:45,166 --> 00:08:46,625
- AND THEN, THEY
MUST'VE SENT OUT

148
00:08:46,708 --> 00:08:49,083
THE UNION'S BEST TO
DEFEAT THE UNKNOWNS,

149
00:08:49,166 --> 00:08:51,750
AND THAT MEANT RALPH WEREC.

150
00:08:51,833 --> 00:08:54,041
- MY BROTHER DIDN'T HAVE
ANY IDEA WHAT WAS HAPPENING.

151
00:08:54,916 --> 00:08:57,375
HE WASN'T TOLD ANYTHING.

152
00:08:57,458 --> 00:09:00,625
HE WAS UNDER THE IMPRESSION
THEY WERE UNMANNED DEAGUE UNITS.

153
00:09:03,625 --> 00:09:05,333
IT WAS ONLY AFTER
MY BROTHER DESTROYED

154
00:09:05,416 --> 00:09:08,708
THE LAST MOBILE WEAPON
THAT HE LEARNED THE TRUTH.

155
00:09:08,791 --> 00:09:09,791
- ONE TO GO.

156
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,041
NOW IT'S DONE.

157
00:09:19,708 --> 00:09:20,708
( gasps )

158
00:09:24,041 --> 00:09:26,708
- WAIT A MINUTE, SOMETHING
DOES NOT MAKE SENSE.

159
